OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWidely very
OL,6,Fwarm and sunny during the early
OL,7,Fevening, although localised thundery
OL,8,Fdownpours are possible in areas north
OL,9,Fand west of Greater London.
OL,10,FThunderstorms largely easing by late
OL,11,Fevening to leave another warm and
OL,12,Fmuggy night with light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FMainly dry and sunny again
OL,15,Fwith temperatures still well above
OL,16,Faverage, especially in the west where
OL,17,Fit will remain hot. Fresher conditions
OL,18,Fexpected near eastern coasts with
OL,19,Fstronger onshore breezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
